		<div class="panel-body" style="margin-top:-15px;padding-top:0px;">
			<div class="col-sm-7 col-sm-push-3 lead" style="text-align:justify">
			  Allows development and operation teams to view and configure applications hosted across multiple servers. Reduces problems associated with adding, removing, and updating values across multiple servers and/or multiple enviroments.  Helps prevent premature deployment or misdeployment of settings.  Designed to support environments where critical settings are affected by regulatory compliance concerns (e.g. separation of duties)
			</div>
			<div class="row"> </div>
			<div class="col-sm-7 col-sm-push-3" style="list-style:square">
