	<div class="panel" id="divTokenServer">
		<div class="panel-heading">
			<h1 class="text-center"><span class="fa fa-cubes"></span><br><span style="font-size:smaller">Token Server</span></h1></div>
		<div class="panel-body" style="margin-top:-15px;padding-top:0px;">
			<div class="col-sm-7 col-sm-push-3 lead" style="text-align:justify">
				Token based authentication/authorization for companies supporting internal service-to-service calls without overhead of OAuth services or other federated identity systems.  Relatively light-weight, yet effective in securing services.   
			</div>
			<div class="row"> </div>
			<div class="col-sm-7 col-sm-push-3" style="list-style:square">
				<ul>
					<li>Supports scoped environments</li>
					<li>Time fenced tokens supports staged deployments</li>
					<li>Single-service multiple-token support</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<ul style="list-style:square">
					<li>Easy integration into existing services</li>
					<li>Uses standard headers</li>
					<li>Cross-service SSO</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

